    üöó Add ‚ÄúReturn Vehicle‚Äù Feature
    Your Vehicle Rental System already supports:

    Adding vehicles

    Updating vehicle details

    Searching vehicles

    Renting vehicles

    User management

    File handling

    Availability tracking

    Now the rental company wants the system to allow returning rented vehicles.

    üéØ Requirements
    Add a new menu option for users:

    4. Return Vehicle
    Show the user a list of their rented vehicles.

    Ask the user which vehicle (by ID) they want to return.

    Mark that vehicle‚Äôs availability as true again.

    Save the updated availability to file.

    Remove or mark the rental from the user‚Äôs rental list:

    Toyota Corolla returned successfully.
    üí° HINTS FOR STUDENTS
    Loop through user.rentals

    Compare rentedVehicle.id with the user‚Äôs input

    If found:

    Set vehicle available = true

    Remove rental from the user‚Äôs rentals list

    Save changes

    Use a boolean variable to track whether a match was found


